  <p>Thank you for your interest in renting with us and for taking the time to complete your application for <strong>{{propertyAddress}}</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info">
  <strong>Application Decision</strong><br>
  After careful review, we regret to inform you that we are unable to approve your application at this time.
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p><strong>Reason for Decision:</strong></p>
  <p style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;">{{reason}}</p>
</div>

{{#if backgroundCheckUsed}}
<div class="info-box">
  <h3>Consumer Reporting Agency Information</h3>
  <div class="message">
    <p>This decision was based in whole or in part on information obtained from a consumer reporting agency:</p>
    <p><strong>{{reportingAgency}}</strong><br>
    {{agencyAddress}}<br>
    Phone: {{agencyPhone}}</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p><strong>Your Rights:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>You have the right to obtain a free copy of your consumer report from the agency within 60 days</li>
    <li>You have the right to dispute the accuracy or completeness of any information in your report</li>
    <li>The reporting agency did not make the decision and cannot explain why it was made</li>
  </ul>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="message">
  <p>We appreciate your interest and wish you the best in finding suitable housing.</p>
</div>

